      <description>
       Revised 1998 version of introduction and overview document for the VO1/VO2-M-VIS-5-DIM-V1.0 PDS3 data
       set, the source data set for all of the reduced (non-EDR) observational data products in this bundle.
       This document deprecates, at least in part, the earlier documents included in this bundle as mdim_mspec_volinfo_1992
       and mdim_dtm_volinfo_1992. Also note that this document is itself partially deprecated. This bundle
       does not follow the directory structure or naming conventions of the original archive volumes, and its member
       products are formatted differently. However, this document offers invaluable information on the
       contents, provenance, and interpretation of the data.

       This document was originally presented as 'document/volinfo.txt' on volumes 15-22 (vo_2015 - vo_2022)
       of VO1/VO2-M-VIS-5-DIM-V1.0. We have discarded its SFDU label; its contents are otherwise unchanged.
      </description>
